name: AVAudioEngineManualRenderingStatus
desc: Status codes that return from the render call to the engine operating in manual rendering mode.

items.name: case error
items.desc: A problem that occurs during rendering and results in no data returning.

items.name: case success
items.desc: A status that indicates the successful return of the requested data.

items.name: case insufficientDataFromInputNode
items.desc: A condition that occurs when the input node doesn’t return enough input data to satisfy the render request at the time of the request.

items.name: case cannotDoInCurrentContext
items.desc: An operation that the system can’t perform under the current conditions.
